                    <span>Are you ready to discard what you learned in school and discover what really motivates people? Are you willing to break out of old, constricting paradigms? Then step forward and meet a master dreamweaver. From the early pages I knew I had found a kindred spirit; hope you feel the same.</span>
                  
              
